author: Pamela Reinsel Cotter
title: The end of Chafee's presidential campaign / Storify
text: The end of Chafee's presidential campaign / Storify Comment Follow @prcotter Posted Oct. 23, 2015 at 5:15 pm Updated at 5:24 PM Lincoln Chafee's early morning announcement Friday that he was dropping out of the 2016 presidential race didn't come to a surprise to many Rhode Islanders or those who follow politics. In this Storify, we take a look and some of the reaction -- often funny, but also heartfelt -- to the former Rhode Island governor's quick burst, and then retreat, from the national political scene.
